for troubled youth? Stand up straight.

943
01:07:46,560 --> 01:07:49,757
All we want is to be
treated like human beings,

944
01:07:49,840 --> 01:07:52,354
not patronised like bunny rabbits.

945
01:07:52,440 --> 01:07:54,590
I don't patronise bunny rabbits.

946
01:07:54,680 --> 01:07:56,671
