they want to be treated like human beings,

951
01:08:10,200 --> 01:08:12,998
it's because they are
being treated like human beings.

952
01:08:13,080 --> 01:08:17,551
Well, I guess I picked the wrong time
to be a human being.

953
01:08:17,640 --> 01:08:19,631
Well, you'll live.

954
01:08:25,760 --> 01:08:27,716
Want some pâté?

955
01:08:27,800 --> 01:08:29,711
