958
01:08:34,760 --> 01:08:37,115
We were doing Chinese at the food fair

959
01:08:37,200 --> 01:08:40,510
when we heard Martha Dumptruck
tried to buy the farm.

960
01:08:40,600 --> 01:08:44,434
