01:09:45,360 --> 01:09:49,273
'Hey, you've got the dog-catcher.'

979
01:09:49,360 --> 01:09:53,717
'My name is Heather.
No... it's not Heather.'

980
01:09:55,000 --> 01:09:57,036
No, it...

981
01:09:58,560 --> 01:10:02,155
It's Madonna. Jeez. No, not that.

982
01:10:02,240 --> 01:10:05,630
Hey, babe, I need a name.

983
01:10:05,720 --> 01:10:07,790
