984
01:10:11,360 --> 01:10:13,271
My name is Tweety.

985
01:10:13,360 --> 01:10:15,316
'Tweety?

986
01:10:16,640 --> 01:10:18,278
'Ooh, tweet! '

987
01:10:18,360 --> 01:10:20,112
God has cursed me, I think.

988
01:10:21,880 --> 01:10:25,714
The last guy I had sex with
killed himself the next day.

989
01:10:28,560 --> 01:10:30,516
